BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 200.4 720 Td (Chapter 4: Param Jaggi) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F4 12 Tf 193.68 698 Td (Age 14 - Invented a CO2 Filter for Cars) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 688 m 540 688 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 660 Td (At 14, Param Jaggi was concerned about car exhaust polluting the air.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 644 Td (He knew that plants convert CO2 into oxygen through photosynthesis.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 628 Td ('What if I could make a device that does what plants do?' he wondered.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 612 Td (He created a device that attaches to car exhaust pipes and uses algae to absorb CO2!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 596 Td (The algae use the CO2 for photosynthesis, converting it to oxygen before it leaves.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 580 Td (His invention won numerous science awards and inspired other young inventors.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 544 Td (THE SCIENCE: AIR PURIFICATION) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 524 Td (Cars produce CO2 when they burn gasoline - a greenhouse gas that warms our planet.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 508 Td (Photosynthesis: plants/algae use CO2 + sunlight + water to make sugar + oxygen.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 492 Td (Algae are incredibly efficient at photosynthesis - even better than trees per volume!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 476 Td (Carbon capture means removing CO2 from the air or exhaust before it enters atmosphere.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 460 Td (Engineers are developing many ways to capture carbon: algae, minerals, and technology.) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 370 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 429 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 409 Td (* A single car produces about 4.6 metric tons of CO2 per year!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 391 Td (* Algae can double their population in just hours - incredibly fast growers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 373 Td (* Trees absorb CO2 but algae can be 10-50 times more efficient per unit area!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 340 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 324 Td (Grow algae! Put pond water in a clear jar in sunlight. In days, green algae will multiply!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 304 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 288 Td (What everyday problems around you could be solved with a creative invention?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
