BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 190.8 720 Td (Chapter 5: Gitanjali Rao) Tj ET
BT 0.4 g /F4 12 Tf 190.8 698 Td (Age 11 - Created a Lead Detection Device) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 688 m 540 688 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 660 Td (When 11-year-old Gitanjali saw news about the Flint, Michigan water crisis,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 644 Td (she was shocked that families were drinking lead-contaminated water without knowing.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 628 Td ('Testing for lead is expensive and slow,' she learned. 'I want to change that!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 612 Td (She invented 'Tethys' - a device that detects lead in water quickly and cheaply.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 596 Td (It uses carbon nanotube sensors that change when lead atoms attach to them.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 580 Td (In 2017, she won the Discovery Education 3M Young Scientist Challenge!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 544 Td (THE SCIENCE: WATER CONTAMINATION) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 524 Td (Lead is a toxic metal that can damage the brain, especially in children.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 508 Td (Old lead pipes can leach lead into drinking water - invisible and tasteless!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 492 Td (Standard lead tests take days and cost hundreds of dollars. Gitanjali's device: seconds!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 476 Td (Carbon nanotubes are tiny tubes of carbon atoms - incredibly sensitive chemical sensors.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 460 Td (The sensor changes electrical resistance when lead atoms bond to it - detectable by a phone!) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 370 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 429 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 409 Td (* Even tiny amounts of lead \(parts per billion\) can harm developing brains.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 391 Td (* Gitanjali was named TIME Magazine's first-ever 'Kid of the Year' in 2020!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 373 Td (* She has since created apps to fight cyberbullying and detect other contaminants.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 340 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 324 Td (Research your local water quality report. What gets tested? Are there any concerns?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 304 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 288 Td (What problems in your community could technology help solve?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
